org.agilewiki.jactor2.core.threading

Class ModuleContext

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.agilewiki.jactor2.core.threading.ModuleContext
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.AutoCloseable

    public final class ModuleContext
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.AutoCloseable
    Provides a thread pool for non-blocking and atomic message processors. Multiple contexts with independent life cycles are also supported. (A ServiceClosedException may be thrown when messages cross contexts and the target context is closed.) In addition, the context maintains a set of AutoClosable objects that are closed when the context is closed, as well as a table of properties.
